            <bug_when>2008-01-22 13:24:18 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>There have been a few attempts in the past by different people to implement an animation lib for qooxdoo. Unfortunately, this task somehow got never finished successfully ...

Anyway, now - as it also fits the development goals for 0.8 quite nicely - we decided to finally add this long-missing feature. Jonathan, a new full-time qooxdoo developer, is currently working on this topic. He&#39;ll keep everybody up-to-date about the state and progress, possibly getting other people involved as well.

The focus is on integrating basic animation features into qooxdoo in two steps, for the two different layers:
1. low-level DOM layer
2. higher-level GUI toolkit (i.e. widgets)

This implementation is targeting 0.8, a backport to 0.7.x is not planned.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
